<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="興福" xml:id="gsz0881c15shiZongLiang"><lb
ed="T" n="0881c15"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0881c15"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012166">明州國寧寺</placeName><persName key="A007279">宗亮</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0881c16"/><persName key="A007279">釋宗亮</persName>，姓<name>馮氏</name>，<placeName key="PL000000012481">奉化</placeName>人也。家傍<placeName key="PL000000049424">月山</placeName>而居，<lb
ed="T" n="0881c17"/>後稱<persName key="A007279">月僧</persName>焉。<persName key="A007279">亮</persName><date notBefore-iso="+0836-01-26" key="j20264282028267" notAfter-iso="+0841-02-07"><name>開成</name>中</date>剃落納法，方事毘<lb
ed="T" n="0881c18"/>尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>，循于四儀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1065"/>，且無遺行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2205"/>。而云我生不辰，屬<lb
ed="T" n="0881c19"/><date from-iso="+0841-02-08" key="j20282682030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25"><name>會昌</name></date>之難，便隱家山深巖洞穴<ptr target="#n3390"/>。<date from-iso="+0847-02-10" key="j20304612035056" to-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大中</name></date>再造<placeName key="PL000000012166">國<lb
ed="T" n="0881c20"/>寧寺</placeName>，徵選清高者隸名，<persName key="A007279">亮</persName>預住持。<placeName key="PL000000018320">建州</placeName>太<lb
ed="T" n="0881c21"/>守<persName key="A008495">李頻</persName>為寺碑云：「於清心行不污者，得二<lb
ed="T" n="0881c22"/>十八人，以補其員。廣住<anchor xml:id="beg0881sgsz5"/>持<anchor xml:id="end0881sgsz5"/>也，律僧<persName key="A007279">宗亮</persName>，禪僧<lb
ed="T" n="0881c23"/><persName key="A013757">全祐</persName>而已。」<placeName key="PL000000012166">國寧</placeName>經藏，載加繕寫，躬求正本，<lb
ed="T" n="0881c24"/>選紙墨，鳩聚嚫施，建造三門藏院諸功德<lb
ed="T" n="0881c25"/>廊宇，皆<persName key="A007279">亮</persName>之力焉。晚年專事禪寂<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2212"/>，不出寺<lb
ed="T" n="0881c26"/>門。處士<ptr type="glossary" target="#g867"/><persName key="A019159">方干</persName>贈詩云：「秋水一泓常見底，㵎<lb
ed="T" n="0881c27"/>松千尺不生枝。空門學佛知多少，剃盡心<lb
ed="T" n="0881c28"/><anchor xml:id="beg0881sgsz7"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0881sgsz7"/>只有師。」終于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000012166">本寺</ref>，春秋八十。<persName key="A007279">亮</persName>恒與沙<lb
ed="T" n="0881c29"/>門<persName key="A013758">貫霜</persName>、<persName key="A013759">棲<anchor xml:id="beg0881001"/>悟<anchor xml:id="end0881001"/></persName>、<persName key="A013745">不吟</persName>數十人，皆秉執清奇，好<pb ed="T" n="0882a" xml:id="T50.2061.0882a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0882a01"/>迭為文會，結林下之交。撰〈嶽林寺碑〉、詩集<lb
ed="T" n="0882a02"/>三百許首<ptr target="#n3393"/>，讚頌並行于代。而於福、敬二田<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2211"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0882a03"/>銳心彌厚焉。<persName key="A007279">亮</persName>為<persName key="A009976"><persName>江東生</persName><persName>羅隱</persName></persName>追慕。<placeName key="PL000000014829">樂安</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0882a04"/><persName key="A013760">孫<anchor xml:id="beg0882sgsz1"/>郃<anchor xml:id="end0882sgsz1"/></persName>最加肯重，著《<placeName key="PL000000012470">四明郡</placeName>才名志》，序諸儒<lb
ed="T" n="0882a05"/>駿士外，獨云：「<persName key="A007279">釋宗亮</persName>多為<anchor xml:id="beg0882sgsz3"/>文<anchor xml:id="end0882sgsz3"/>士先達倣仰<lb
ed="T" n="0882a06"/>焉。」</p>
